<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel=stylesheet type="text/css" href="/style.css">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/7939d32273.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <title>Sitrep</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="title-container">
            <h1>SITREP</h1>
            <h4>Like a status, but collaborative!</h4>
            <hr>
            <p class="description">Sitrep is a collaboration tool designed for Discord servers. Set an activity status in the bot, then let other people see the server's sitrep! One user can have sitrep statuses in multiple servers, so no more need for global status creation that doesn't show duration!</p>
            <hr>
            <div class="invite-container">
                <a href="<%= inviteLink %>" target="_blank" class="invite-link"><button><i class="fab fa-discord icon"></i>Invite!</button></a>
                <a href="<%= githubLink %>" target="_blank" class="invite-link"><button><i class="fab fa-github icon"></i>See the Github!</button></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="howto">
        <h1>
            More Coming Soon . . . 
        </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="contact">

    </div>
</body>
</html>